From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


This is a maintenance category, used for maintenance of the Wikipedia project. It is not part of the encyclopedia and contains non-article pages, or groups articles by status rather than subject. Do not include this category in content categories.ShortcutCAT:ACAT:A
This category contains pages about adminship, the state of being an administrator, including the means of  attaining that state and those who have attained it. Administrators are a group of trusted users with access to certain things not available to other users, for example the ability to delete pages and block users.

For pages related to the general administration of Wikipedia, which are not specific to the group of people called "administrators", see Category:Wikipedia administration.
For a list of users who are administrators, see Category:Wikipedia administrators or Special:Listusers/sysop.
